<p class="c3"><span class="c0">Translation: </span><span class="c1">Don&rsquo;t post any content on Feline Pride that you don&rsquo;t own. If you find something on Feline Pride that belongs to you and was put up without your permission, please contact us using the copyright infringement notice process described here.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">7. Content Posted by Users.</span><span class="c1">&nbsp;We do not promise that information on Feline Pride posted by third parties, including content posted by other users, is accurate or reliable. While we diligently monitor and screen postings to keep Feline Pride suitable for kids, we make no warranties, express or implied, as to the accuracy, reliability, or suitability of any postings. We have no obligation to modify or remove any inappropriate postings, and no responsibility for the conduct of the member submitting any posting. Notwithstanding the foregoing, we, in our sole discretion, reserve the right to prevent any postings from being placed on Feline Pride, and to edit, restrict, or remove such postings for any reason at any time.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">Translation: </span><span class="c1">We work hard to make Feline Pride a safe place for kids, but a lot depends on our players. LionHaus is not responsible for content on Feline Pride posted by users or other third parties. However, if we think content is not appropriate, we can take it down at any time without asking for permission.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">8. No Hacking. &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">You agree not to post any content that contains viruses, corrupted files, or any other similar software or programs that may harm Feline Pride or make it operate poorly, or that would do the same to a third-party computer or any other specific feature of Feline Pride. You also agree that you will not decompile, disassemble or copy Feline Pride or any of its source code or network transmissions. If you violate this rule we will remove you as a user and block you from using Feline Pride. Doing so, however, does not limit our other rights and remedies. Also, you understand that by breaking this rule, you will have irreparably harmed us and Feline Pride.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">Translation: </span><span class="c1">Don&rsquo;t ruin it for everyone else by trying to hack, copy or reverse engineer all or part of Feline Pride. Also, don&rsquo;t share viruses, or corrupted links or files with Feline Pride or Feline Pride users.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">9. Termination. &nbsp;</span><span class="c1">We may, in our sole discretion and with or without warning, cease operation of Feline Pride, terminate your membership to Feline Pride, or otherwise restrict your access to Feline Pride. Furthermore, should we find any user breaking our rules, we reserve the right to suspend or delete associated accounts and take any other action we deem appropriate.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">Translation: </span><span class="c1">We can suspend or terminate your Feline Pride account and the game itself at any time, with or without any notice to you.</span></p>
<p class="c3"><span class="c0">10. License to Use Feline Pride. </span><span class="c1">We grant you the non-exclusive, non-transferable, non-sublicensable, limited right and license to access Feline Pride for personal, non-commercial use. Your rights are subject to your compliance with this TOS agreement. The term of your license starts on the date that you install or otherwise use Feline Pride, and ends on the earlier of you ceasing use of Feline Pride or our terminating your license. Your license terminates immediately if you violate the law or attempt to circumvent any technical protection measures used in connection with Feline Pride.</span></p>
